    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, zest half your<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>lemon[s]</strong> (try to grate lightly with a micro-plane or sharp box grater and avoid grating the white pith, as this is very bitter)</p><p>Roll the <strong>lemon[s] </strong>with your hand on a hard surface (to release more juice) and cut in half</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
