    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>honey</strong>, <strong>wholegrain mustard</strong>, <strong>dried oregano </strong>and<strong> </strong>1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span><strong> vegetable oil </strong>with the juice of half the<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>lemon[s] </strong>in a small bowl</p><p>Season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your<strong> honey mustard marinade</strong></p>",
