      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> chicken breast portion[s]</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) (use <strong>tin foil </strong>to avoid mess!) and drizzle over the <strong>honey mustard marinade</strong>, then<strong> </strong>give everything a good mix up</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 18-20 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!) – there are your <strong>baked honey mustard chicken breast[s]</strong></p>",
